  "message": "ci: run only lib tests in dist workflow to avoid missing binary\n\nIntegration tests require the dcg binary which isn't built until after the\ntest job. Run --lib tests only in the dist workflow.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
